headline: 3 Residential REITs Worth Considering Amid Market Headwinds
summary: Despite macroeconomic uncertainty and choppy consumer confidence, healthy rental demand amid favorable demographics and high homeownership costs poise Zacks Equity REIT - Residential industry players like EQR, ESS and UMH well for growth.
